An error ocurred in WebApps: \"${ error.msgid: An error ocurred in WebApps: "${ error }", see details below.
msgstr: Ett fel inträffade i WebApps: "${ error }", se detaljerna nedan.

An Error Occurred - Available Applicatio.msgid: An Error Occurred - Available Applications | Turris
msgstr: Ett fel inträffade - Tillgängliga applikationer | Turris

More detailed information is available i.msgid: More detailed information is available in the console of your web browser - on most browsers accessible after pressing <kbd>Ctrl+Shift+J</kbd> or <kbd>F12</kbd>.
msgstr: Mer detaljerad information finns tillgängligt i din webbläsares konsol - kan nås i de flesta webbläsarna genom att man trycker <kbd>Ctrl+Shift+J</kbd> eller <kbd>F12</kbd>.

Please report this error to our support.msgid: Please report this error to our support team via e-mail: tech.support@turris.cz.
msgstr: Vänligen rapportera det här felet till vårat hjälpteam via e-post: tech.support@turris.cz.

Switching to the default one in: ${ time.msgid: Switching to the default one in: ${ timeLeft } sec.
msgstr: Byter till den huvudsakliga om: ${ timeLeft } sek.

Turris is developed by CZ.NIC, the CZ do.msgid: Turris is developed by CZ.NIC, the CZ domain registry.
msgstr: Turris utvecklas av CZ.NIC, registret för CZ-domänen.
